* Extraction\nTypes
** Full Extraction
***_ Reads entire dataset each run
***_ Good for small volumes
***_ No change tracking needed
***_ Rebuild tables periodically
** Incremental Extraction
***_ Only new/changed records
***_ Needs change indicator (timestamp/version)
***_ State management required
***_ Handles late-arriving records
** Streaming Extraction
***_ Near real-time capture
***_ Continuous processing
***_ Seconds/minutes latency
***_ Always-on infrastructure
@endmindmap
